OL,5, Customer service standards at energy   
OL,6, companies have fallen to a record low  
OL,7, as households are being hit by soaring 
OL,8, bills, Citizens Advice has said.       
OL,10,FStandards have "plummeted" since June  
OL,11,F2021 when several suppliers went bust  
OL,12,Fdue to high global gas prices, it said.
OL,14,FThe average waiting time on the phone  
OL,15,Fto speak to a firm is now about six and
OL,16,Fa half minutes, compared to just under 
OL,17,Ffour minutes the year before.          
OL,19,FCitizens Advice called for improvements
OL,20,Fbefore bills rise again in the autumn. 
